{"tid":638664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山男倒斃　血流引水道","createTime":"2018-04-23T02:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T02:11:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4104bd4b232d781dc81172de1cbcb66df0ba9183","tid":638664,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20370355?_ga=2.41650850.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20370355%3F_ga%3D2.41650850.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=wSxIb2v5vvFDpzmX%2FKbEVjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a51b889b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F20370355%3F_ga%3D2.41650850.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=722399ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180423/20370355?_ga=2.41650850.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n行山男倒斃　血流引水道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門青榕台對上麥理浩徑第10段，昨晨約5時56分，一名姓彭53歲男子，倒臥約兩米引水道下，頭部流血昏迷，行山人士發現報警。消防及救護員到場，證實男事主已經死亡。警方現場撿獲死者銀包身份證及財物，懷疑失足跌落引水道，頭部撞向石壆昏迷，失救致死。初步調查沒有可疑，死因有待剖屍化驗。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n女司機公路暈低　Smart溜後撼寶馬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【有片有真相】司機清白全靠車Cam"}]}